<title>HRAMTHAWKNAK HLA CH507</title>
<key>G</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Pa, Fapa le Thiang Thlarau cungah thanthat nak zungzal um ko seh,
 Hramthawk can ah a rak si bang, Zungzal in a si ko lai, Dong hin loin,
 A-men.</lyrics>
